OL,6,FThe defendant, who had 921 followers
OL,7,Fon the platform, was drunk when he
OL,8,Fmade the recording.
OL,10,FJudge Carolyn Scott, sentencing, said:
OL,11,F"The wording used by you in that
OL,12,FTikTok video was hugely offensive and
OL,13,Fdangerous.
OL,15,F"You referenced people who practise
OL,16,FIslam as being largely responsible for
OL,17,Fawful crimes committed in this country.
OL,19,F"You spoke about asylum seekers in a
OL,20,Fdespicable way.
