OL,4,Cdown city's mosques in TikTok video
OL,6,F"You stated that you and others at the
OL,7,Fplanned march in Newcastle would burn
OL,8,Fdown every mosque in Newcastle."
OL,10,FAfter he was arrested, he told police:
OL,11,F"No-one can say anything these days."
OL,13,FThe judge said the video was made at a
OL,14,Ftime when there was widespread
OL,15,Fviolence in the country and the
OL,16,Frecording was meant to encourage
OL,17,Fothers to act.
