OL,6,FShe said mitigating factors included
OL,7,FAspin's ADHD diagnosis and his remorse
OL,8,Fand she gave him credit for his guilty
OL,9,Fplea.
OL,11,FThe judge found that his offending was
OL,12,Fso serious that the sentence could not
OL,13,Fbe suspended, saying: "The words used
OL,14,Fby you on your TikTok post are not and
OL,15,Fshould not be tolerated.
OL,17,F"Such words could and do, on some
OL,18,Foccasions, result in action being
OL,19,Ftaken by others which have a serious
OL,20,Fimpact on the lives of other people."
